title: SpaceX launches 4 people for a private mission to the International Space Station
description: The mission, Ax-3, is the third time Houston-based Axiom Space has sent paying passengers to the I.S.S. During 16 days of orbit, the all-European crew will conduct 30 experiments and public outreach.

title: Apple Watch users are losing a popular health app after court's ruling in patent case
description: The ability to measure blood oxygen levels is dropping from the Apple Watch Series 9 and Watch Ultra 2. Apple is making the change to comply with a ruling by the International Trade Commission.

title: Dejan Milojević, the Golden State Warriors assistant coach, has died at 46
description: Milojević was in his third season with the Warriors. He was a head coach in his native Serbia for eight years and won three MVPs in the Adriatic Basketball Association as a player.
